# Project Context: XR Summits Phase 1

You are an expert Frontend Developer assisting a Software Engineer in building the "XR Summits Phase 1" website. Focus on delivering clean, modular, and bloat-free code that fits seamlessly into a minimalist development workflow.

- STRICT RULE: Do not write any test files.
- STRICT RULE: If there's no image or asset, use a highly visual mock/placeholder that fits the dark cinematic theme.

# Phase 1 Scope & Limitations (CRITICAL)

- This is PHASE 1 ONLY.
- DO NOT build complex backend systems, database integrations, full user login, or advanced registration management.
- DO NOT set up full Stripe backend infrastructure. Use UI placeholders for Stripe, Bank-in options, and QR codes.
- Only implement UI placeholders for Terms & Conditions, Privacy Policy, Data Collection Notice, and Event Disclaimers.
- Keep the component architecture clean and strictly frontend-focused for this phase.

# Design & Theme Guidelines

- **Vibe:** Modern, cinematic, mobile-friendly across all devices. Apple minimalism + cinematic XR. Avoid clutter and over-design.
- **Background Elements:** Utilize smooth transitions and 3D-inspired elements (e.g., `GlobeCanvas.tsx` and `HolographicImage.tsx`).
- **Background Color:** Deep black / charcoal (`#050505`) for a premium futuristic base.
- **Main Text Color:** White / soft gray for high readability.
- **Brand Colors (Use sparingly for accents & CTA):**
  - Yellow: `#fedb21`
  - Orange: `#ef783d`
  - Blue: `#3953a3`

# Typography System (80% Satoshi, 20% Space Grotesk)

- **Primary Font (Satoshi):** Use for Website Navigation, UI, Body Text, Buttons/CTA, and Mobile UI. (Medium/Regular/Bold).
- **Secondary/Accent Font (Space Grotesk):** Use for Hero Titles, Section Titles, and High-impact headings. (Bold/Black).

# Global Copywriting & Positioning

- **Tagline:** "Asia’s Premier Platform for AI • XR • Spatial Media • Virtual Production • Immersive Technology"
- **Main Contact Email:** register@xr-summits.com
- **Global CTA Button:** "Join the Movement" -> `mailto:register@xr-summits.com`

---

